Excellent.  I remember going to this midnight movie once back in the 70's and watching a documentary on CSNY.   Holy crap, was everyone baked back then or what.  Seriously!  If kids did half the stuff we did back in the day it would be utter hysteria.  Young was a crazed rebel back then so he split.  He wasn't a crazed out as Joe Walsh however.  That dude was out there!
Dude thats all you got of CSN! Please remind me to up some more thats so sad... they are great! and there so many more albums in my collection

the pot was low potency, the lsd highly potent. we were all baked back 'then' and tripped at the drop of a hat. the pot today though is far superior and the acid is junk. ride a bike a long way, then bathe. it feels just as good to be healthy....peace.
